Package seng201.islandtradergame.core

Class Route

java.lang.Object
seng201.islandtradergame.core.Route
public class Route
extends java.lang.Object
This class implements a Route which specifies the route from one island to another. These routes are shared by two islands.
Author:
Kei Carden

    • oneOfIslands

      public boolean oneOfIslands​(Island island)
      Checks to see if the parsed in island is the same as any of the islands in this route. If the island is the same as islandOne then they traders current island is island one and wants to travel to islandTwo. islandTravlingTo becomes the second island if islandTwo is the same as the current island then islandTravlingTo becomes islandOne.
      Parameters:
      island - The island the routes want to be found for
      Returns:
      boolean Whether the island is part of this route or not

    • getRouteDistance
